      "value": "<p>Once per day, an ifrit can cast @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.Item.a2zXJ84rzkD8SIBe]{Overheat} as a spell-like ability. At 8th level, he can use this ability one additional time per day, and he gains a third use per day at 16th level. His caster level equals his level, and the save DC is equal to 11 + his Charisma modifier.</p>\n<p><em>After adding the spell to the Spellbook tab, edit the spell's Details, changing the Spell Preparation Mode to Innate Spellcasting, and change Limited uses to x of x Day as level allows. Use the formula</em><em>(11 + @abilities.cha.mod) in the Saving Throw field.</em></p>"
